tweet: As the child of migrant workers, many thought I could never get into Georgetown Univ. I took the chance & filled out the application. I urge students to reach for the stars & apply to the universities they really to go to. Nothing ventured, nothing gained!  https://bit.ly/2V4gOev

I introduced the bipartisan Border Patrol Pay Security Act of 2019. This legislation would allow our men & women in green to qualify for overtime pay under the Fair Labor Standards Act, ensuring pay parity w/ other law enforcement agencies. Read more here: https://bit.ly/2L8obgH

Yesterday I joined the @stcjaguars President, Dr. Shirley A. Reed, in announcing the educational partnership opportunities the college has made with the @DHSgov agencies to allow federal law enforcement academy graduates to be granted college credit. pic.twitter.com/PegJdITrQY

Today I announced the awarding of $2 Million for Webb County’s Veterans Court Program, which serves #veterans & their families in the counties of Webb, Starr, & Zapata. The funding benefit veterans w/ individualized treatment for substance use disorders.   https://bit.ly/2DwfjuO  pic.twitter.com/U4543ZqvsU

U.S. International Trade Commission report shows that U.S.-Mexico-Canada Trade Agreement #USMCA will increase economic activity by 0.35% and create 176,000 new jobs. Congress needs to approve this agreement fast. Read my full statement here:  https://bit.ly/2Gp0UBf  pic.twitter.com/5oMeCXztbn
